---
import Icon from './Icon.astro'
---

<section class="box skills">
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="terminal-window"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Full Stack</h2>
    <p>
      With expertise in both frontend and backend development, I deliver
      cohesive, end-to-end solutions that bridge the gap between user experience
      and server-side functionality. My full stack capabilities ensure seamless
      integration, high performance, and scalability in every project I
      undertake.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon icon="trophy" color="var(--accent-regular)" size="2.5rem" gradient />
    <h2>Industry Leader</h2>
    <p>
      As a thought leader in the tech community, I consistently stay ahead of
      industry trends, contributing innovative solutions and insights. My
      commitment to excellence and continuous learning has established me as a
      trusted expert in Full Stack JavaScript development.
    </p>
  </div>
  <div class="stack gap-2 lg:gap-4">
    <Icon
      icon="strategy"
      color="var(--accent-regular)"
      size="2.5rem"
      gradient
    />
    <h2>Strategy-Minded</h2>
    <p>
      I excel at aligning technical solutions with business objectives, ensuring
      that each project not only meets but exceeds strategic goals. My
      analytical approach and strategic thinking drive impactful results,
      optimizing performance and delivering measurable value.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .box {
    border: 1px solid var(--gray-800);
    border-radius: 0.75rem;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    background-color: var(--gray-999_40);
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .skills {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3rem;
  }

  .skills h2 {
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  .skills p {
    color: var(--gray-400);
  }

  @media (min-width: 50em) {
    .box {
      border-radius: 1.5rem;
      padding: 2.5rem;
    }

    .skills {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
      gap: 5rem;
    }

    .skills h2 {
      font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    }
  }
</style>
